  <entry>
    <id>https://www.thunderbird.net/en-US/thunderbird/147.0/releasenotes/</id>
    <title type="html">Thunderbird 147.0</title>
    <author>
      <name>Thunderbird</name>
      <uri>https://www.thunderbird.net</uri>
    </author>
    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.thunderbird.net/en-US/thunderbird/147.0/releasenotes/"/>
    <updated>2026-01-13T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <published>2026-01-13T00:00:00+00:00</published>

    <content type="html"><![CDATA[
      

  
  

  
    

    
      
        
        

        
          <h3>What’s New</h3>
        

        
        
          <ul>
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Add "Show Full Path" folder pane option for compact view modes</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Add `mail.useLocalizedFolderNames' to toggle special folder name localization</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        
          </ul>
        

        
          <h3>Changed</h3>
        

        
        
          <ul>
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Special folders are now localized based on a restricted set of names</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        
          </ul>
        

        
          <h3>Fixed</h3>
        

        
        
          <ul>
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Selected status and priority was not displayed in search widgets</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Compacting multiple folders failed and did not compact</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Resetting manual folder sorting did not work for sub folders</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Unified archive subfolders could show wrong names and no messages</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Folders with deep hierarchy and long folder names could fail to display</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Moving saved search/virtual folder under IMAP could fail</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>"Open and Show" for OpenPGP-signed message (.eml) did not work</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>"Search Messages" search did not finish due to unparsable local folders</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Compose command line flag no longer worked correctly</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Search for "Attachment" in Settings menu did not find "Files and Attachments"</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Account Hub did not show error message on failure when creating OAuth2 EWS account</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Thunderbird could crash during exchange address account setup</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Japanese locale users could not create message filters</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Moving virtual folder within maildir based IMAP or local folder could fail</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Thunderbird could crash when marking all messages as read</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Startup could be slow with large number of folders not using subscriptions</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>EWS message send that required a password errored instead of prompting</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>EWS HTTP 500 backoff errors were not handled gracefully</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>SMTP sending could hang when when multiple messages queued for sending</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Thunderbird could crash when emptying EWS trash</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Broken feed icon could prevent updating of feeds</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Calendar did not alert user for connection issues</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Creation of tasks with Start or Due date was not possible</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Visual and UX improvements</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p><a href="https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/security/known-vulnerabilities/thunderbird/#thunderbird147">Security fixes</a></p>
          
        </li>
      
    
    </ul>
  
  

<p>As always, you’re encouraged to <a href="https://connect.mozilla.org/t5/ideas/idb-p/ideas/label-name/thunderbird">tell us what you think</a>, <a href="https://support.mozilla.org/questions/new/thunderbird">ask for help</a>, or <a href="https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/enter_bug.cgi?product=Thunderbird">file a bug in Bugzilla</a></p>
<style> li p { display: inline; } </style>
      ]]>
    </content>
  </entry>
  
